* Pre-FixedPositions or Manually (use Editor_Mode and Enable_Visible_Points to set fixed and anchor manually) [heavy on mobile]

* Collisions [are extremely simple and unstable, but they work] (for box and sphere, just add the desired objects to the list. For Mesh, in addition to adding the list,
