* Wind (Direction, strength, etc.... there's not much of a secret,bruh) [Note: Wind is a feature I added mostly for my own testing, so it's very simple and global, meaning it point in the same direction independently]

*Seam_Constraints (used to weld points and vertices in the same place, useful in specific situations with models) 

A few more things... you'll figure out what they're for yourself...lol


 most of the variables are already pre-set, but still.... try to test it your way :)
